headline: Prediction: 2 Brilliant Stocks Will Be Worth More Than Palantir Technologies by Year's End in 2025
summary: Palantir Technologies (NASDAQ: PLTR) shares have advanced 360% this year, outpacing the next closest stock in the S&P 500 (SNPINDEX: ^GSPC) by 100 percentage points.  The data analytics company is now worth $180 billion, but certain Wall Street analysts expect Shopify (NYSE: SHOP) and Uber Technologies (NYSE: UBER) to surpass that figure before year's end in 2025.  Shopify is currently worth $140 billion.

headline: Three Reasons We Love Uber (UBER)
summary: Over the past six months, Uber’s shares (currently trading at $61.04) have posted a disappointing 14.1% loss, well below the S&P 500’s 8.8% gain. This might have investors contemplating their next move.
